abstract: Israeli authorities report fatal shooting of two Palestinians who drove their cars into soldiers in separate incidents in West Bank.
lead_paragraph: The Israeli authorities said troops shot and killed two Palestinians who had rammed their cars into soldiers.

headline.main: West Bank: Palestinians Killed After Attacks on Troops
headline.print_headline: Middle East; West Bank: Hit-and-Run Attacks
